"TC-VITAL-0052","Vitals & Observations","FHIR-BP-Component","Verify blood pressure is represented as components under LOINC 85354-9","FHIR","Integration","P2","High","Medium","FHIR R4 endpoint; a BP Observation exists","1. GET the blood pressure Observation | 2. Inspect components","Panel LOINC=85354-9; Systolic=8480-6; Diastolic=8462-4","BP Observation has code 85354-9 with two components (systolic 8480-6, diastolic 8462-4), each with mmHg UCUM units","Automatable","REQ-VITAL-026","Standards-FHIR; Clinical","Standards"
