"TC-VITAL-0054","Vitals & Observations","HL7-ORU","Verify inbound HL7 v2 ORU vital result maps to an observation","HL7","Integration","P2","High","High","HL7 v2 interface configured; adapter ingests ORU R01 messages","1. Send an ORU^R01 with OBX vital-sign segments | 2. Process the message | 3. Verify the created observation","OBX|1|NM|8867-4^Heart rate^LN||72|/min; PID with patient identifier","ORU message is parsed; OBX maps to the correct vital observation with value 72 and unit; patient matched via PID","Manual-Only","REQ-VITAL-027","Standards-HL7; Clinical; Data Integrity","Standards"
