"TC-VITAL-0063","Vitals & Observations","Exploratory-Locale","Explore decimal separator and locale handling on input","Exploratory","Regression","P3","Medium","Medium","Logged in as Clinician; browser locale set to a comma-decimal locale","1. Switch browser/app locale | 2. Enter a decimal vital using locale separator | 3. Save | 4. Verify stored value","Temperature=37,5 in a comma-locale","Value is interpreted correctly as 37.5 (or input is clearly validated); no silent misinterpretation as 375","Manual-Only","REQ-VITAL-011","Data Integrity; Patient Safety","Platform"
