"TC-APPT-0001","Appointment Scheduling","Book Appointment","Book an appointment with valid patient, provider, service, location and future time slot","Functional","Smoke","P1","Critical","High","Logged in as Scheduler at a session location; an active patient, a bookable service, a provider and a location exist","1. Open the Appointment Scheduling app | 2. Search and select the active patient | 3. Click Add new appointment | 4. Select the service | 5. Select the provider | 6. Select the location | 7. Select a future date and an available time slot | 8. Set status Scheduled | 9. Click Save","Patient=Jane Synthetic (ID=10001V); Service=General Medicine; Provider=Dr A Tester; Location=Outpatient Clinic; Date=02-Jul-2026; Time=10:00","Appointment is created with a unique appointment ID, status Scheduled, and appears on the patient's appointment list and the provider's day view with the selected service, location and time","Automatable","REQ-APPT-001","Clinical; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
