"TC-APPT-0004","Appointment Scheduling","Past-Date Prevention","Prevent booking an appointment in the past","Negative","Regression","P1","Critical","High","Logged in as Scheduler; patient selected; current date is 01-Jul-2026","1. Select the patient | 2. Select service, provider and location | 3. Choose a date earlier than today | 4. Attempt to choose a time slot | 5. Click Save","Patient=Jane Synthetic (ID=10001V); Service=General Medicine; Date=29-Jun-2026; Time=09:00","System prevents booking in the past with a clear validation message; no appointment is created","Automatable","REQ-APPT-003","Patient Safety; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
"TC-APPT-0005","Appointment Scheduling","Past-Date Prevention","Boundary - booking exactly at the current date and time edge","Boundary","Regression","P2","High","Medium","Logged in as Scheduler; patient selected; server clock at 01-Jul-2026 09:00","1. Select patient, service, provider, location | 2. Choose today's date | 3. Select the earliest slot at or just after the current time | 4. Click Save","Patient=Jane Synthetic (ID=10001V); Date=01-Jul-2026; Time=09:15","Slot at or after current time is accepted and saved; any slot before current time is rejected","Partially-Automatable","REQ-APPT-003","Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
"TC-APPT-0006","Appointment Scheduling","Conflict Prevention","Prevent double-booking the same provider in an overlapping time slot","Negative","Integration","P1","Critical","High","Logged in as Scheduler; provider Dr A Tester already has an appointment 10:00-10:30 on 02-Jul-2026","1. Select a different patient | 2. Select same provider and service | 3. Select date 02-Jul-2026 and an overlapping slot 10:15 | 4. Click Save","Patient=Mark Synthetic (ID=10002V); Provider=Dr A Tester; Date=02-Jul-2026; Time=10:15","System detects the provider time conflict and blocks the save or warns; the overlapping appointment is not silently created","Partially-Automatable","REQ-APPT-004","Patient Safety; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
"TC-APPT-0007","Appointment Scheduling","Conflict Prevention","Decision table - conflict handling across provider, location and patient overlaps","Decision Table","Regression","P2","High","High","Logged in as Scheduler; existing appointment 10:00-10:30 for Provider P1, Location L1, Patient Pt1","1. Attempt overlapping booking varying provider, location and patient as per data rows | 2. Observe whether conflict is raised for each combination | 3. Record the outcome","Rule1 sameProvider+sameTime=conflict; Rule2 sameLocation+sameTime+diffProvider=warn; Rule3 samePatient+sameTime=conflict; Rule4 allDifferent=allowed","Each rule resolves to its expected outcome: provider and patient overlaps are blocked, location-only overlaps warn, and fully distinct bookings are allowed","Partially-Automatable","REQ-APPT-004","Patient Safety; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
"TC-APPT-0008","Appointment Scheduling","Conflict Prevention","Prevent the same patient being booked into two overlapping appointments","Negative","Regression","P2","High","Medium","Logged in as Scheduler; patient already has appointment 10:00-10:30 on 02-Jul-2026","1. Select the same patient | 2. Select a different provider and service | 3. Choose an overlapping slot at 10:10 | 4. Click Save","Patient=Jane Synthetic (ID=10001V); Provider=Dr B Tester; Date=02-Jul-2026; Time=10:10","System warns or blocks the overlapping patient appointment to avoid a patient being in two places at once","Partially-Automatable","REQ-APPT-004","Patient Safety; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
"TC-APPT-0009","Appointment Scheduling","Provider Selection","Filter providers by selected service before booking","Functional","Regression","P3","Medium","Medium","Logged in as Scheduler; services mapped to specific providers","1. Select the patient | 2. Select a specialty service | 3. Open the provider dropdown | 4. Verify only providers offering that service are listed","Service=Cardiology; ExpectedProviders=Dr Cardio One, Dr Cardio Two","Only providers associated with the selected service are shown; unrelated providers are not selectable","Automatable","REQ-APPT-002","Clinical","OpenMRS"
