"TC-APPT-0011","Appointment Scheduling","Time Slot","Boundary - book the first and last available slot of an availability block","Boundary","Regression","P2","Medium","Medium","Logged in as Scheduler; provider availability 09:00-12:00 with 30-min slots","1. Book the earliest slot at 09:00 | 2. Save | 3. Book the last slot at 11:30 | 4. Save | 5. Attempt to book 12:00","Provider=Dr A Tester; Date=03-Jul-2026; Slots=09:00, 11:30, 12:00","First (09:00) and last (11:30) slots are bookable; the slot at the boundary end 12:00 outside the block is not offered or is rejected","Partially-Automatable","REQ-APPT-005","Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
