"TC-HL7-0019","HL7 v2 Messaging","Malformed-Rejection","Reject a truncated message cut off mid-segment","Negative","Regression","P1","High","High","MLLP listener running","1. Send a message that ends abruptly inside the PID segment | 2. Observe handling | 3. Check acknowledgment and queue","MSH|...|ADT^A01|MSG0019|P|2.5; PID|1||PAT123 (stream truncated, no segment terminator)","Message is rejected/quarantined as incomplete, no partial patient data is filed, and a NAK or error is logged","Automatable","REQ-HL7-012","Data Integrity; Patient Safety; Standards-HL7","Standards"
"TC-HL7-0020","HL7 v2 Messaging","Malformed-Rejection","Reject a message containing non-printable control characters in a data field","Security","Regression","P2","High","Medium","MLLP listener running; input sanitization enabled","1. Send an ADT^A08 with embedded null/control bytes in PID-5 | 2. Observe handling | 3. Check stored demographics and acknowledgment","PID-5 contains Doe^Jo\\x00hn with an embedded NUL byte","Message is rejected or the control characters are safely stripped/escaped, no corrupted data is stored, and the event is logged","Partially-Automatable","REQ-HL7-013","Security; Data Integrity; Standards-HL7","Standards"
"TC-HL7-0021","HL7 v2 Messaging","Duplicate-Handling","Detect and suppress a duplicate message with a repeated MSH-10 control ID","Functional","Regression","P1","High","High","MLLP listener running; duplicate detection enabled; message MSG0021 already processed successfully","1. Re-send the identical ADT^A01 with the same MSH-10 | 2. Observe handling | 3. Verify encounter count","Resent MSH-10=MSG0021; identical ADT^A01 payload","Duplicate is detected and not re-processed (no second encounter created), an idempotent AA ACK is returned, and the duplicate is logged","Automatable","REQ-HL7-014","Patient Safety; Data Integrity; Standards-HL7","Standards"
