"TC-HL7-0027","HL7 v2 Messaging","PID-Demographics","Validate PID-7 birthdate boundary values (min and max plausible dates)","Boundary","Regression","P2","Medium","Medium","MLLP listener running; date validation enabled","1. Send an ADT^A04 with the earliest plausible DOB | 2. Send another with a far-future DOB | 3. Compare handling","DOB-A=PID-7=18800101; DOB-B=PID-7=20990101 (future)","The valid historical DOB is accepted; the future DOB is rejected or flagged per business rule, with an appropriate ACK/NAK in each case","Partially-Automatable","REQ-HL7-016","Data Integrity; Standards-HL7","Standards"
