"TC-HL7-0029","HL7 v2 Messaging","Datetime-Format","Validate TS datetime fields with timezone offset are parsed correctly","Functional","Integration","P2","Medium","Medium","MLLP listener running; engine timezone configured","1. Send ADT^A01 with a fully qualified timestamp including offset | 2. Confirm consumption | 3. Verify stored encounter time in local zone","PV1-44 admit datetime=20260701123045-0500","Timestamp is parsed with the -0500 offset and stored/displayed correctly normalized, and an AA ACK is returned","Partially-Automatable","REQ-HL7-017","Data Integrity; Clinical; Standards-HL7","Standards"
