"TC-TELE-0014","Telemedicine","Video Session","Media permission decision table across camera and mic states","Decision Table","Regression","P2","Medium","Medium","Patient on supported browser with controllable permissions","1. Set camera/mic to each combination | 2. Join | 3. Record resulting mode | 4. Repeat for all four combinations","Combos: (cam=Y mic=Y)->AV; (cam=N mic=Y)->Audio; (cam=Y mic=N)->blocked; (cam=N mic=N)->blocked","AV when both allowed; audio-only when only mic allowed; session blocked with guidance when mic denied regardless of camera","Partially-Automatable","REQ-TELE-005","Clinical","Platform"
