"TC-ENC-0026","Encounters & Clinical Forms","Encounter Roles","Assign a provider to a specific encounter role and verify storage","Functional","Regression","P2","High","Medium","Logged in clinician; provider directory populated; encounter roles configured (Clinician, Consultant); active visit","1. Start an encounter | 2. Assign Provider A to role Clinician | 3. Assign Provider B to role Consultant | 4. Save","RoleClinician=ProviderA; RoleConsultant=ProviderB","Both provider-role assignments are stored on the encounter and shown distinctly on the encounter view","Partially-Automatable","REQ-ENC-030","Clinical; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
