"TC-ENC-0030","Encounters & Clinical Forms","Retrospective Entry","Record a retrospective encounter with a backdated encounter datetime within the visit window","Functional","Regression","P2","High","Medium","Logged in clinician with retrospective entry privilege; visit spanning a past date range","1. Open the patient | 2. Start a retrospective encounter | 3. Set encounter datetime to a past date inside the visit | 4. Save","EncounterDate=visitStart+1day (past)","The encounter is saved with the backdated datetime and is associated with the correct visit","Partially-Automatable","REQ-ENC-040","Clinical; Data Integrity; Audit","OpenMRS"
"TC-ENC-0031","Encounters & Clinical Forms","Retrospective Entry","Backdated encounter datetime cannot precede the visit start","Boundary","Regression","P2","High","Medium","Logged in clinician; visit with a defined start datetime","1. Start a retrospective encounter | 2. Set encounter datetime before the visit start | 3. Attempt save","EncounterDate=visitStart-1day","Save is blocked with a validation message that the encounter must fall within the visit window","Partially-Automatable","REQ-ENC-041","Clinical; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
