"TC-ENC-0035","Encounters & Clinical Forms","Form Entry","Conditional (skip-logic) field appears only when its trigger answer is selected","Functional","Regression","P2","Medium","Medium","Logged in clinician; form with conditional field shown when Pregnant=Yes; active visit","1. Start the form | 2. Verify the conditional gestational-age field is hidden | 3. Set Pregnant=Yes | 4. Verify the field appears","Trigger: Pregnant=Yes","The conditional field is hidden by default and revealed only when the trigger answer is selected","Partially-Automatable","REQ-ENC-015","Clinical; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
