"TC-ENC-0043","Encounters & Clinical Forms","API","Create an encounter with observations via REST and verify the persisted resource","API","Integration","P2","High","Medium","Valid REST credentials; patient uuid and active visit uuid known; encounter type uuid known","1. POST to /ws/rest/v1/encounter with encounterType, patient, visit, encounterDatetime and obs array | 2. Capture response | 3. GET the created encounter","API=REST encounter create","HTTP 201 with an encounter uuid; GET returns the encounter with the submitted obs and provider data","Automatable","REQ-ENC-060","Standards-FHIR; Data Integrity; Clinical","OpenMRS"
"TC-ENC-0044","Encounters & Clinical Forms","API","REST encounter create rejects a missing required encounterType","Negative","Integration","P2","High","Medium","Valid REST credentials; patient uuid known","1. POST to /ws/rest/v1/encounter omitting encounterType | 2. Inspect response","API payload missing encounterType","HTTP 400 with a validation error naming encounterType; no encounter is created","Automatable","REQ-ENC-061","Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
