"TC-ENC-0056","Encounters & Clinical Forms","Accessibility","Clinical form fields are reachable and operable via keyboard only","Accessibility","Regression","P2","High","Medium","Logged in clinician; a multi-field clinical form; keyboard only","1. Open the form | 2. Tab through every field in logical order | 3. Operate dropdowns, date pickers and checkboxes via keyboard | 4. Save via keyboard","Input=keyboard only","Every control is reachable in a logical tab order and fully operable without a mouse; save succeeds","Manual-Only","REQ-ENC-100","Accessibility","OpenMRS"
