"TC-CONSENT-0058","Consent & Privacy","Authorization Checks","Security: consent decision cannot be bypassed via parameter tampering","Security","System","P1","Critical","High","API reachable; user with no research consent on target patient","1. Issue a denied research request | 2. Tamper purpose/scope params and resubmit | 3. Try alternate ids and verbs","Tamper purpose=Treatment for research","All tampered variants are denied or correctly scoped server-side; client-supplied purpose cannot override server policy and attempts are logged","Partially-Automatable","REQ-CONSENT-017","Security; PHI/Privacy","Standards"
"TC-BILL2-0001","Billing (deep)","Charge Master","Create a new chargeable item in the charge master with all mandatory attributes","Functional","Regression","P1","High","High","Billing admin logged in with charge-master management privilege","1. Open charge master maintenance | 2. Add a new chargeable item | 3. Enter code, description, unit price, department and effective date | 4. Save","Code=LAB-CBC; Desc=Complete Blood Count; UnitPrice=25.00; Dept=Laboratory; EffectiveDate=2026-07-01","Item is persisted and appears in charge master search with the correct active price and effective date","Automatable","REQ-BILL2-001","Billing; Data Integrity","Platform"
"TC-BILL2-0002","Billing (deep)","Charge Master","Reject charge master item with negative unit price","Negative","Regression","P1","High","High","Billing admin logged in with charge-master privilege","1. Add a new chargeable item | 2. Enter a negative unit price | 3. Attempt to save","Code=LAB-XYZ; UnitPrice=-10.00","Save is blocked with a validation error that unit price must be zero or greater; no item is created","Automatable","REQ-BILL2-001","Billing; Data Integrity","Platform"
"TC-BILL2-0003","Billing (deep)","Charge Master","Reject duplicate charge code in charge master","Negative","Regression","P2","High","Medium","An item with code LAB-CBC already exists","1. Add a new chargeable item | 2. Enter an existing code LAB-CBC | 3. Save","Code=LAB-CBC (duplicate)","Save is blocked with a uniqueness violation message; no duplicate row is created","Automatable","REQ-BILL2-001","Billing; Data Integrity","Platform"
