"TC-BILL2-0008","Billing (deep)","Itemized Invoice","Generate itemized invoice from posted encounter charges","Functional","Integration","P1","Critical","High","Patient has a closed visit with lab, pharmacy and consultation charges posted","1. Open the patient billing | 2. Generate invoice for the visit | 3. Review line items","Charges=Consult 50.00, CBC 25.00, Amoxicillin 12.50","Invoice lists each charge as a separate line with quantity, unit price and line total; subtotal equals 87.50","Automatable","REQ-BILL2-010","Billing; Data Integrity","Platform"
