"TC-BILL2-0011","Billing (deep)","Itemized Invoice","Invoice subtotal, tax and grand total reconcile","Functional","Integration","P1","Critical","High","Draft invoice with three line items and a tax rule of 5%","1. Review subtotal | 2. Review tax | 3. Review grand total","Subtotal=100.00; Tax=5%","Tax equals 5.00; grand total equals 105.00; sum of line totals equals subtotal","Automatable","REQ-BILL2-011","Billing; Data Integrity","Platform"
