"TC-BILL2-0013","Billing (deep)","Itemized Invoice","Finalized invoice cannot be edited; only adjustment allowed","State Transition","Regression","P1","Critical","High","Invoice in Finalized state","1. Open finalized invoice | 2. Attempt to edit a line | 3. Observe available actions","State=Finalized","Direct edit is disabled; only credit/adjustment workflow is available; original lines are immutable","Automatable","REQ-BILL2-012","Billing; Audit; Data Integrity","Platform"
