"TC-RESTAPI-0046","REST API (deep, per resource)","Query Params","startIndex beyond total returns empty results not an error","Boundary","Regression","P2","Medium","Low","A resource collection with a known small total (e.g. 3 patients matching)","1. GET /patient?q=Test&limit=10&startIndex=1000 | 2. Inspect results and total","startIndex=1000 (beyond total)","HTTP 200 with an empty results array and the correct totalCount; no error is thrown","Automatable","REQ-RESTAPI-014","Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
