"TC-FHIR2-0005","FHIR R4 (deep: search/bundle/operations)","Search Params - Patient","Boundary - Patient birthdate equality vs prefix search","Boundary","Regression","P2","Medium","Medium","Patients with birthdate 1990-01-01 and 1990-12-31 exist","1. GET /Patient?birthdate=1990-01-01 | 2. GET /Patient?birthdate=ge1990-01-01&birthdate=le1990-12-31 | 3. Compare result sets","birthdate=1990-01-01; ge1990-01-01; le1990-12-31","Exact match returns only same-day; range with ge/le returns full-year set inclusively; boundary dates included","Automatable","REQ-FHIR2-003","Standards-FHIR;Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
