"TC-FHIR2-0011","FHIR R4 (deep: search/bundle/operations)","Common Params - _sort","Sort search results ascending by _lastUpdated","FHIR","Regression","P2","Medium","Medium","Multiple resources with differing lastUpdated","1. GET /Patient?_sort=_lastUpdated | 2. Verify ascending order of meta.lastUpdated across entries","_sort=_lastUpdated","HTTP 200; entries ordered ascending by lastUpdated; ties stable","Automatable","REQ-FHIR2-006","Standards-FHIR;Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
