"TC-COMPAT-0009","Cross-Browser & Compatibility","OS Compatibility","Pairwise coverage of Browser x OS combinations for login","Pairwise","Regression","P1","High","Medium","Multiple browser/OS test rigs available; valid account","1. Execute login on each pairwise cell (Chrome/Win, Firefox/macOS, Edge/Win, Safari/macOS, Chromium/Linux) | 2. Record pass/fail per cell | 3. Capture screenshots | 4. Compare","Pairs=Chrome-Win11; Firefox-macOS; Edge-Win10; Safari-macOS; Chromium-Linux","Login succeeds across all pairwise cells; no combination-specific authentication failure","Partially-Automatable","REQ-COMPAT-005","Security; Clinical","OpenMRS"
