"TC-COMPAT-0015","Cross-Browser & Compatibility","Browser Zoom","Verify layout integrity at 200 percent browser zoom (WCAG 1.4.4)","Accessibility","Regression","P2","High","Medium","Clinician account; accessibility requirement","1. Open patient dashboard | 2. Set browser zoom to 200% | 3. Verify all content and functionality available | 4. Check no content loss or overlap","Zoom=200%; Browser=Firefox","All content readable and operable at 200% zoom without horizontal scrolling for primary content; meets WCAG 1.4.4","Partially-Automatable","REQ-COMPAT-009","Accessibility","Standards"
