"TC-COMPAT-0028","Cross-Browser & Compatibility","Cookie & Session","Verify behavior when third-party cookies are blocked","Negative","Regression","P2","Medium","Medium","Browser configured to block third-party cookies","1. Block third-party cookies in browser settings | 2. Log in | 3. Use core flows | 4. Verify no broken embedded content or SSO","Browser=Safari (ITP); Setting=block third-party cookies","First-party session functions; any third-party embeds degrade gracefully with clear messaging; no silent failure","Manual-Only","REQ-COMPAT-013","Security; Clinical","OpenMRS"
