"TC-INTEG-0009","Integration (cross-module & external)","Visit to Encounter Linkage","Encounters created across modules link to the same active visit","Functional","Integration","P2","High","Medium","Patient has one active visit; vitals, notes and orders configured","1. Start active visit | 2. Add vitals encounter | 3. Add a consultation note encounter | 4. Place an order (creates order encounter) | 5. Review visit summary","Patient=SYN-1002","All three encounters appear under the single active visit with the same visit id; no orphan encounters created","Automatable","REQ-INTEG-005","Clinical;Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
