"TC-TELE2-0034","Telemedicine (deep)","Cross-Device","Browser/OS pairwise matrix for join compatibility","Pairwise","Regression","P2","Medium","Medium","Test lab with multiple browser/OS/network combinations","1. For each pairwise combination join a session | 2. Verify media establishes | 3. Record outcome","Pairs: Chrome/Win/WiFi, Safari/iOS/4G, Firefox/Mac/WiFi, Edge/Win/Ethernet, ChromeAndroid/4G","Each pairwise combination establishes media and core controls function; any unsupported combo shows a clear unsupported-browser message pre-join","Manual-Only","REQ-TELE2-017","Clinical","Platform"
