"TC-TELE2-0038","Telemedicine (deep)","Security/Privacy","Join link is single-use/time-bound and rejects reuse after session","Security","Regression","P1","Critical","High","A completed or expired telehealth visit with its join link","1. Complete a session | 2. Attempt to reopen the same join link | 3. Attempt to use an expired link","Link state: used / expired","Reusing a consumed or expired link is rejected with a safe message; no unauthorized re-entry into the prior session; attempt is audited","Partially-Automatable","REQ-TELE2-019","Security; PHI/Privacy; Audit","Platform"
