"TC-DATAQ-0025","Data Quality & Migration","Referential Integrity","Negative: load order violation creates dangling reference and is caught","Negative","Integration","P1","Critical","High","Loader configured with dependency ordering; test injects out-of-order load","1. Attempt to load encounters before their parent patients | 2. Observe loader behavior | 3. Inspect integrity check result","Encounter batch references patient IDs not yet loaded","Loader either defers/queues the dependent rows or fails fast; integrity check reports the dangling references; no committed orphan rows remain","Automatable","REQ-DATAQ-007","Data Integrity","Platform"
