"TC-DATAQ-0040","Data Quality & Migration","Migration via HL7","HL7 v2 ADT feed loads historical admissions with correct PID mapping","HL7","Integration","P2","High","High","HL7 v2 ADT^A01 inbound interface configured to a parsing/loader pipeline","1. Submit a batch of ADT^A01 messages with PID, PV1 segments | 2. Process through the loader | 3. Verify patient identity (PID-3), name (PID-5), admission (PV1) in target","ADT^A01 with PID-3=MRN12345, PID-5=Tester^Pat, PV1 admit datetime","Each ADT message creates/updates the correct patient and visit; PID-3 maps to identifier, PID-5 to name, PV1 to visit; malformed segments are rejected with NAK","Partially-Automatable","REQ-DATAQ-020","Standards-HL7; Data Integrity","Standards"
