"TC-DATAQ-0048","Data Quality & Migration","Transformation Rules","Truncation guard: source value longer than target column is rejected not silently cut","Negative","System","P2","High","Medium","Target column has fixed max length; transform has length guard","1. Load a row whose name field exceeds the target column length | 2. Run the transform | 3. Inspect stored value and reject behavior","Source name length=300; target max=255","The over-length value is rejected (or routed to remediation) rather than silently truncated to 255; reason captured; data integrity preserved","Automatable","REQ-DATAQ-011","Data Integrity","Platform"
