"TC-DEATH-0007","Death & Record Lifecycle","Mark Deceased - Date Boundary","Accept a death date equal to the current system date (boundary today)","Boundary","Regression","P2","Medium","Medium","Clinician on a living patient","1. Open Mark Patient Deceased | 2. Set Dead=Yes | 3. Enter Death Date = today | 4. Select valid cause | 5. Save","Today=2026-07-01; Death Date=2026-07-01","Save succeeds; death date today is accepted as the upper boundary","Automatable","REQ-DEATH-002","Clinical; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
