"TC-PORTAL-0011","Patient Portal & Self-Service","View Results","Lab result release hold (embargo) before clinician review","Decision Table","Integration","P1","Critical","High","Result release policy with embargo for sensitive/abnormal results configured","1. Generate normal, abnormal, and sensitive results | 2. Apply release rules | 3. View patient portal results list","Normal -> immediate; Abnormal -> embargo until review; Sensitive(HIV/genetic) -> manual release","Each result type follows its release rule; embargoed results are hidden until released; released-at timestamp and releaser are audited","Partially-Automatable","REQ-PORTAL-008","Clinical; Patient Safety; PHI/Privacy; Audit","Platform"
