"TC-PORTAL-0013","Patient Portal & Self-Service","Book Appointment","Book an appointment in an available slot","Functional","System","P2","High","Medium","Appointment scheduling enabled; bookable provider/service with open slots","1. Log in | 2. Open Appointments | 3. Select service and provider | 4. Pick an open slot | 5. Confirm booking","Service=Primary Care; Provider=Dr. Lee; Slot=2026-07-10 09:00","Appointment is created and visible to patient and clinic schedule; confirmation is shown; slot is no longer offered to others","Automatable","REQ-PORTAL-009","Clinical; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
"TC-PORTAL-0014","Patient Portal & Self-Service","Book Appointment","Prevent double-booking of the same slot under concurrent requests","Negative","Integration","P1","Critical","High","Single open slot; two portal sessions attempting the same slot","1. Open the same slot in two sessions | 2. Confirm booking in session A | 3. Confirm booking in session B near-simultaneously","Slot=2026-07-10 09:00; SessionA; SessionB","Only one booking succeeds; the second receives a slot-unavailable error; no overbooking and no orphaned hold remains","Partially-Automatable","REQ-PORTAL-009","Patient Safety; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
"TC-PORTAL-0015","Patient Portal & Self-Service","Book Appointment","Booking boundary at clinic lead-time and scheduling horizon","Boundary","Regression","P3","Medium","Medium","Min lead time (e.g., 2h) and max horizon (e.g., 90 days) configured","1. Attempt booking 1 min before min lead time | 2. Attempt exactly at min lead time | 3. Attempt at max horizon | 4. Attempt 1 day beyond horizon","MinLead=2h; Horizon=90d","Bookings inside lead time and beyond horizon are rejected; exactly-at-boundary bookings are accepted","Automatable","REQ-PORTAL-009","Data Integrity","Platform"
