"TC-PORTAL-0017","Patient Portal & Self-Service","Cancel Appointment","Block self-cancellation after the cancellation cutoff","Negative","Regression","P3","Medium","Medium","Appointment within the no-self-cancel cutoff window","1. Open an appointment inside cutoff | 2. Attempt to cancel","ApptId=APPT-556; Cutoff=2h before start","Self-cancellation is blocked with guidance to contact the clinic; appointment remains Booked; attempt is logged","Automatable","REQ-PORTAL-010","Clinical; Data Integrity","Platform"
"TC-PORTAL-0018","Patient Portal & Self-Service","Appointment State","Appointment lifecycle state transitions are valid only along allowed paths","State Transition","Integration","P2","High","Medium","Appointment workflow with states Requested/Booked/CheckedIn/Completed/Cancelled/NoShow","1. Drive appointment through each transition | 2. Attempt illegal transitions (e.g., Completed -> Booked) | 3. Verify final states","Transitions per state model","Only allowed transitions succeed; illegal transitions are rejected; terminal states cannot revert; each change is timestamped and audited","Partially-Automatable","REQ-PORTAL-010","Data Integrity; Audit","Platform"
