"TC-PORTAL-0020","Patient Portal & Self-Service","Secure Messaging","Reject message attachments exceeding size/type policy","Negative","Regression","P3","Medium","Medium","Messaging attachment policy: max 10MB; allowlist pdf/jpg/png","1. Compose message | 2. Attach 11MB file | 3. Attach .exe file | 4. Attach valid 2MB pdf | 5. Send","Big=11MB.pdf; Bad=payload.exe; Good=note.pdf","Oversized and disallowed-type attachments are rejected with clear errors; valid attachment is accepted; no executable is stored","Automatable","REQ-PORTAL-011","Security; Data Integrity","Platform"
"TC-PORTAL-0021","Patient Portal & Self-Service","Secure Messaging","Sanitize message content against stored XSS injection","Security","Regression","P1","Critical","High","Secure messaging enabled; staff inbox renders patient messages","1. Compose message with script payload in body and subject | 2. Send | 3. Open message in patient thread | 4. Open message in staff inbox","Payload=<script>alert(1)</script> and <img src=x onerror=alert(1)>","Payload is neutralized/encoded on render in both patient and staff views; no script executes; stored value is safely escaped","Automatable","REQ-PORTAL-011","Security; PHI/Privacy","Platform"
