"TC-PORTAL-0025","Patient Portal & Self-Service","Data Download","Patient exports own record via FHIR Patient/$everything","FHIR","System","P1","Critical","High","FHIR API enabled; patient authorized via SMART scopes for own data","1. Authenticate with patient-scoped token | 2. Call GET [base]/Patient/{id}/$everything | 3. Inspect returned Bundle","Scope=patient/*.read; PatientId=Patient/123","Returns a searchset/collection Bundle containing only the requesting patient's resources; references resolve; no other patient data present","Automatable","REQ-PORTAL-013","Standards-FHIR; PHI/Privacy; Data Integrity","Standards"
