"TC-PORTAL-0027","Patient Portal & Self-Service","Data Download","Bulk Data export kickoff returns 202 with Content-Location polling","FHIR","Integration","P2","High","Medium","FHIR Bulk Data ($export) enabled; backend authorization (SMART backend services)","1. POST [base]/$export with Prefer: respond-async | 2. Capture Content-Location | 3. Poll status endpoint until complete | 4. Download NDJSON files","Header: Prefer=respond-async; _type=Patient,Observation","Kickoff returns 202 with Content-Location; polling returns in-progress then 200 with output file manifest; files are valid NDJSON per resource type","Automatable","REQ-PORTAL-014","Standards-FHIR; Data Integrity","Standards"
