"TC-PORTAL-0033","Patient Portal & Self-Service","Proxy/Minor Access","Revoke a previously granted proxy and verify access denial","Negative","Regression","P2","High","High","Active proxy relationship between proxy P and patient X","1. Admin/patient revokes proxy | 2. Proxy P logs in | 3. Proxy attempts to open patient X profile","Proxy=P-200; Patient=X-2003","Revoked proxy can no longer view patient X data; attempt returns access denied and is audited; no cached PHI is served","Partially-Automatable","REQ-PORTAL-015","Security; PHI/Privacy; Audit","Platform"
